3. What I Would Do Differently With More Time
If more development time were available, several improvements could be made to enhance the system.
More advanced natural language understanding
Instead of keyword-based intent detection, the system could use more advanced techniques such as intent classification and entity extraction. This would allow the agent to handle more complex business questions and generate richer insights.
Data visualization
Currently, the results are primarily displayed as counts and tables. Adding visualizations such as pipeline stage charts, sector distribution graphs, and execution status dashboards would make insights easier to interpret, especially for leadership users.
Performance improvements
For larger boards, additional optimizations such as API pagination handling, caching frequently accessed data, and background data refresh processes could improve performance and scalability.
