4. Bonus Feature – Leadership Updates Interpretation
For the bonus requirement, I interpreted “leadership updates” as concise executive-level summaries of business performance, particularly focused on the sales pipeline.
The agent generates a leadership-style update that includes:
•	Total number of deals in the pipeline
•	Distribution of deals by stage
•	Distribution of deals by status
•	Sector breakdown of deals
In addition to these metrics, the agent produces simple automated insights such as identifying the pipeline stage with the highest number of deals and highlighting deals currently in negotiation or already converted into work orders.
The goal of this feature is to simulate the type of high-level summary that leadership teams might review during regular business or sales update meetings.

